Key Match Events: The Bulls gave up the most points to any opponent thus far this season to a Jazz team that came in averaging a league-worst 99.8 points per game.
Post-Match Reflections: Ayo Dosunmu performed well starting in place of Zach LaVine.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Bulls handed the Jazz their first win of the season.
Others: Lauri Markkanen and Jordan Clarkson were both missing for the Bulls.
